high_descs: Walk straight towards the microwave.
Pick up the yellow knife to the left of the microwave.
Turn around and head towards the black circle table.
Slice the lettuce closest to you in several pieces.
Put the knife on the table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn around and head towards the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the fridge, let it cool, and take it back out.
Turn around and head towards the table.
Place the lettuce to the right of the knives on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put the yellow knife along with the cool slice lettuce on the black round table.

high_descs: Turn and go to the counter by the microwave.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and go to the round table.
Slice a head of lettuce on the table.
Put the knife on the table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Put the slice of lettuce in the refrigerator and take the slice of lettuce out of the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the round table.
Put the slice of lettuce on the round table.
anns.task_desc: Chill a slice of lettuce in the refrigerator.

high_descs: cross the room to the counter with the knives to the left of the microwave
take the knife that is next to the loaf of bread
turn around and cross the room to the far wall, then turn left to face the table
slice the lettuce located nearest the center of the table
place the knife on the table to the right of the salt
take a slice of lettuce from the table
turn around and move to stand in front of the refrigerator
open the door, and place the slice of lettuce next to the apple on the top shelf. Close the door and wait 7 seconds. Open the door, remove the slice of lettuce, and close the refrigerator door again.
turn left, and return to your previous position in front of the lettuce on the grey table
place the lettuce on the table, at the bottom of the handle of the knife pointed at the potted plant.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool slice of lettuce on the table

high_descs: Turn left, go straight to the counter, turn right, go straight to the counter.
Take the large knife from the counter.
Turn around, go straight, turn left at the round black table.
Cut the lettuce closest to the plant on the table into slices.
Put the knife on the table to the right of the closest pepper mill.
Take a slice of lettuce from the table.
Turn around, go to the fridge to the forward right.
Put the slice of lettuce to the left of the tomato in the fridge. Close then open the fridge. Take the lettuce from the fridge.
Turn left, go back to the black round table.
Put the lettuce to the right of the large knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of lettuce on a table.

high_descs: Walk forward across the room to face the counter to the left of the microwave.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn around and walk across the room then turn left to face the kitchen table.
Cut the top green vegetable on the table.
Put the knife on the table.
Pick up a slice of the vegetable that was cut.
Turn around and walk forward to face the fridge.
Cool the slice of vegetable in the fridge and then remove it.
Turn around and walk forward to face the table.
Put the slice of vegetable on the right side of the table.
anns.task_desc: To cut a vegetable, cool a slice of it, as well as place it on the table.
